          body {
              font-family: 'Avenir Roman', sans-serif;
              color: #2a2a2a;
              font-size: 1.6rem;
              padding: 0;
              margin: 0;
          }

              body * {
                  outline: none !important;
                  box-sizing: border-box;
              }

                  body *:focus {
                      outline: none !important;
                  }

              body a {
                  text-decoration: none;
              }

                  body a:hover,
                  body a:focus {
                      text-decoration: none;
                  }

              body ol,
              body ul {
                  margin-bottom: 20px;
              }

              body p {
                  font-size: 16px;
                  color: #2a2a2a;
                  line-height: 22px;
                  margin: 0 0 20px;
              }

              body h1 {
                  color: #6f358d;
                  font-family: 'Avenir Black', sans-serif;
                  font-size: 43px;
                  margin: 10px 0;
                  padding: 0px;
              }

              body header {
                  width: 100%;
                  position: fixed;
                  top: 0;
                  left: 0;
                  z-index: 11;
              }

                  body header .top-header {
                      display: table;
                      width: 100%;
                  }

                  body header .left,
                  body header .right {
                      display: table-cell;
                      vertical-align: bottom;
                  }

                  body header .logo {
                      display: block;
                  }

                      body header .logo img {
                          height: 50px;
                      }

                  body header .wis-logo {
                      float: right;
                  }

                  body header .header-wrap {
                      background-color: #ffffff;
                      border-bottom: 1px solid #d7d7d7;
                      padding: 15px 50px;
                  }

              body div[role="main"] {
                  padding-top: 85px;
                  background-color: #f4f7fa;
              }

                  body div[role="main"] section.banner {
                      height: 200px;
                      background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,');
                      background-size: cover;
                      background-position: center;
                  }

                  body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page {
                      max-width: 900px;
                      padding: 10px 20px;
                      margin: 0 auto;
                      text-align: center;
                      display: -webkit-flex;
                      display: flex;
                      -webkit-flex-direction: column;
                      flex-direction: column;
                      justify-content: center;
                      min-height: calc(100vh - 375px);
                  }

                      body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page > * {
                          display: block;
                      }

                      body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page a {
                          color: #6f358d;
                          text-decoration: underline;
                      }

                      body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page ul.social-media-link {
                          list-style-type: none;
                          padding: 0;
                          margin: 15px 0;
                          text-align: center;
                      }

                          body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page ul.social-media-link li {
                              display: inline-block;
                          }

                              body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page ul.social-media-link li + li {
                                  margin-left: 15px;
                              }

                              body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page ul.social-media-link li a {
                                  display: block;
                                  width: 40px;
                                  height: 40px;
                                  border-radius: 50%;
                              }

                                  body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page ul.social-media-link li a.facebook {
                                      background-color: #06465e;
                                  }

                                      body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page ul.social-media-link li a.facebook img {
                                          height: 23px;
                                          margin-top: 8.5px;
                                      }

                                  body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page ul.social-media-link li a.twitter {
                                      background-color: #2b6d85;
                                  }

                                      body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page ul.social-media-link li a.twitter img {
                                          height: 17px;
                                          margin-top: 11.5px;
                                      }

                                  body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page ul.social-media-link li a.youtube {
                                      background-color: #af232d;
                                  }

                                      body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page ul.social-media-link li a.youtube img {
                                          height: 25px;
                                          margin-top: 7.5px;
                                      }

                      body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page .countdown-box {
                          background-color: #ffffff;
                          padding: 25px 30px 30px;
                          border-radius: 20px;
                          display: inline-block;
                      }

                          body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page .countdown-box p {
                              margin-bottom: 0px;
                          }

                          body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page .countdown-box .number {
                              color: #6f358d;
                              font-family: 'Avenir Black', sans-serif;
                              font-size: 36px;
                          }

              body footer {
                  padding: 35px 20px 30px;
                  border-top: 1px solid #ebeef4;
                  background-color: #6f358d;
              }

                  body footer .left {
                      text-align: center;
                  }

                      body footer .left span {
                          display: block;
                          margin-bottom: 10px;
                          color: #ffffff;
                          font-size: 12px;
                      }

                          body footer .left span b {
                              font-family: 'Avenir Black', sans-serif;
                          }

          @media (max-width: 991px) {
              body div[role="main"] section.banner {
                  height: 255px;
              }
          }

          @media (max-width: 767px) {
              body header .header-wrap {
                  padding: 15px 20px;
              }

              body header .logo img {
                  height: 30px;
              }

              body header .logo-gov img {
                  height: 20px;
              }

              body div[role="main"] {
                  padding-top: 67px;
              }

                  body div[role="main"] section.banner {
                      height: 110px;
                  }

              body h1 {
                  font-size: 36px;
              }

              body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page {
                  padding: 10px;
              }

                  body div[role="main"] section.content-redirect-page .countdown-box {
                      display: block;
                      padding: 25px 15px;
                  }
          }
      </style>
    <!-- script-->
  </head>
  <!-- body-->
  <body onload="startTime()">
    <!-- header-->
    <!-- page header-->
    <header>
      <div class="header-wrap">
        <div class="top-header">
          <div class="left">
            <a href="#" class="logo">
              <img src="data:image/png;base64,">
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="right">
            <div class="wis">
              <div class="wis-logo">
                <a href="#" class="logo-gov">
                  <img src="data:image/png;base64,">
                </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <div role="main">
      <section class="banner"></section>
      <section class="content-redirect-page">
        <p style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>The Media Development Authority is now the <br>Info-communications Media Development Authority (IMDA).</strong></p>
        <p>IMDA will develop a vibrant, world-class infocomm media sector that drives the economy, connects people, bonds communities and powers Singapore's Smart Nation vision.</p>
        <div class="countdown-box">
            <p>This page will be automatically redirected to <a href="https://www.imda.gov.sg/">IMDA Homepage</a> in</p>
            <div class="number" id="time">10</div>
            <p>seconds</p>
            
        </div>
        <!-- social media-->
        <ul class="social-media-link">
          <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/IMDAsg" target="_blank" class="facebook"><img src="data:image/png;base64,"></a></li>
          <li><a href="https://twitter.com/IMDAsg" target="_blank" class="twitter"><img src="data:image/png;base64,"></a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/imdasg" target="_blank" class="youtube"><img src="data:image/png;base64,"></a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
    <!-- footer-->
    <footer>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="left"><span class="copyright">Copyright &copy; Info-communications Media Development Authority</span></div>
      </div>
    </footer>
    <script>
        function startTime() {
            var timer = 10;
            var seconds;
            var display = document.querySelector('#time');
            var countdown = setInterval(function () {
                seconds = parseInt(timer % 60, 10);
                display.textContent = seconds;

                if (--timer < 0) {
                    clearInterval(countdown);
                     window.location = "https://www.imda.gov.sg/";
                }
            }, 1000);
        }
    </script>
  </body>
